Subject: AHA Badge Soldering
Description: Its a yearly tradition to for All Hands Active to bring a special badge soldering project. There are two projects to choose from this year, a quick and easy option and a more complex one. Kits are available for purchase. All proceeds go directly to AHA.  Speakers include:AHA - Track: Penguicon  - Duration: 4 hours
